title: Ebook Foothold of Tethys 4 of 4
description:
Part 4 of 4 science fiction Ebook Foothold of Tethys.

 With prolonged spaceflight becoming a reality through the hydrogen engine and the ample water supply found in the belts of Jupiter, the human race has expanded into the solar system. But as slowly markets for transported goods skyrocket, the ones now living on the new frontier, the largest space station orbiting Jupiter's moon Tethys, find themselves between the strict Earth rulership and a renegade invasion.

This book is totally FREE with the compliments of the writer. Read it, share it, and if you like it, buy the book to help the writer.

If you liked this book, it might be interesting to know that a prequel called 'Children of the Moon' is being worked on.
